{"tid":996290,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"iOS開show無人講？","createTime":"2019-01-26T07:20:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T17:08:24.000Z","uid":525,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"49fae4e140d26e76d04888a6cc6bcb2089cf243b","tid":996290,"uid":525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T07:20:22.000Z","msg":"CVE PRESENT:<br />\nINSTINCT OF SIGHT「BLENDED ABSTRACT」DEBUT CD RELEASE PARTY<br />\n<br />\n[ 感性透徹 五年醞釀 ]<br />\n<br />\nInstinct of Sight 呈獻首張份量大碟《Blended Abstract》<br />\n大碟將收錄足本十首歌曲，包括多首未發佈作品。本專輯由樂隊親自監製，以五味雜陳的紋理還原最真緻的我們。<br />\n標誌性的雙聲融合在爆炸與變幻莫測的音場中；<br />\n躁動、細膩、解放音樂和畫面結合的可能性。<br />\n這是一張目前的我們最無可挑剔的專輯。<br />\n<br />\n三月九日<br />\n為大家送上有史以來<br />\n最完整的 Instinct of Sight<br />\n萬事俱備 只欠你們<br />\n觀能撼擊 只此一場<br />\n浩瀚征途 始於此地<br />\n<br />\nInstinct of Sight proudly presents the definitive collection &ldquo;Blended Abstract&rdquo;. <br />\nConsisting of 10 tracks and unreleased songs. This album is the culmination of years of work. A masterpiece of audio supervised in painstaking detail by the band.  <br />\n<br />\nThe journey begins here. Available on March 9th.<br />\n<br />\n日期 Date: 9 March 2019 (SAT)<br />\n時間 Time: 19:30 (DOORS OPEN)<br />\n地點 Venue: Musiczone@Emax<br />\n地址 Address: 九龍灣國際展貿中心地下 <br />\n1 Trademark Drive, Kowloon Bay<br />\n特別嘉賓 Special Guest: 鐵樹蘭 Tie Shu Lan<br />\n<br />\nEvent Link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/299022967422589/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F299022967422589%2F&d=kyUqZPIW%2FdI4el07YyYQ5y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=ee6ae52d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/299022967422589/</a><br />\n<br />\n票價 Tickets: <br />\n$400 (預售+大碟 Advance + CD)<br />\n$280 (預售 Advance)<br />\n$320 (即場 Walk-in)<br />\n<br />\n[ 門票現已公開發售 ]<br />\n網上售票 Online Ticketing: [<a href=\"https://tickcats.co/ticket/ios]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftickcats.co%2Fticket%2Fios%5D&